The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v Richard J. Setmeyer, Defendant-Appellant.No. 57784First District (5th Division)July 20, 1973.PER CURIAM.John S. Wrona and S. David Friedlander, of Calumet City, for appellant.Bernard Carey, State’s Attorney, of Chicago, (Kenneth L. Gillis and Daniel Murray, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel,) for the People.

Rehearing denied September 18, 1973.

LORENZ, J., took no part.
